text: Ashraful Abedin is a Jatiya Party (Ershad) politician and the former Member of Parliament of Jhenaidah-2. ==Career== Abedin was elected to parliament from Jhenaidah-2 as a Jatiya Party candidate in 1988. ==References== Category:Living people Category:4th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Jatiya Party (Ershad) politicians
title: Ashraful Abedin
